#: {{ux|en|Sorry, I '''mistook''' you for my brother. You look very similar.}}
#: {{ux|en|Don't '''mistake''' my kindness for weakness.}}
#* {{circa|1597}} {{w|William Shakespeare}}, ''{{w|Henry IV, Part 2}}'', Act IV, Scene 2,<sup>[http://www.opensourceshakespeare.org/views/plays/play_view.php?WorkID=henry4p2&Act=4&Scene=2&Scope=scene]</sup>
